@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_umydtj(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v1
    v1 = v2
    v2 = wp.exp(0.50)
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.86)) + 0.21)
    v0 = v2
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.cos((v0 + 0.91 / tmp + 0.19)))
    v2 = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.51) * (v0 + 0.19 * tmp + 0.62)) / (v0 - (v1 + 0.99 * v1 + 0.97)))
    data[tid] = v0
